{"tid":1212064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想訓又訓唔到","createTime":"2019-06-12T17:13:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T17:36:38.000Z","uid":198624,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"db3d908f0bee20de62ef94c4393cfdc3ae70d717","tid":1212064,"uid":198624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:13:13.000Z","msg":"發夢今日去左示威<br />\n朝早去搬路障<br />\n下晝食左幾飛催淚彈好撚辛苦<br />\n眼淚鼻水係咁流<br />\n然後淆底得濟走左嚇醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家喺張床上想訓覺<br />\n一合埋眼<br />\n耳仔就響起今日示威嘅人嘅吶喊<br />\n諗起d人中煙難受嘅樣<br />\n仲有警犬嘅一連串惡行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗到呢到，個心不由自主咁痛，訓唔到<br />\n痛係因為我唔明點解我地年青人要承受咁大嘅痛苦，我地又做錯左d咩呀，我地為嘅其實只係香港呢個家，香港人呢個身份啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我諗呢個夢仲未完<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc218ab4bbf38bad470a3a8ac1c2bba03011853a","tid":1212064,"uid":258091,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:18:10.000Z","msg":"個夢長過你 不過想訓又訓唔到same"},{"pid":"971771be2c4808a97f9d6779c0d95cf3c8d203df","tid":1212064,"uid":46488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:19:06.000Z","msg":"There&rsquo;s no light<br />\nWe will walk in darkness"},{"pid":"34691d2fa73fb46c8b88655ec34120e8d96ba7d6","tid":1212064,"uid":114945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:19:19.000Z","msg":"去過現場既人乜訓得著咩"},{"pid":"61081d43b5502b52cb5398e4152adfa88ad5115d","tid":1212064,"uid":182022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:19:42.000Z","msg":"I know that feel bro <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700f51926269227d658e385cff8d9e2e4f1c3321","tid":1212064,"uid":185781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,